## Installation

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8 or higher
- pip package manager

### Step 1: Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/iki-breathing-app.git
cd iki-breathing-app
```

### Step 2: Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install pygame
```

### Step 3: Add Music Files
Place your MP3 music files in the `assets/music/` directory:
```
assets/
└── music/
    ├── sleep.mp3      # 174 Hz frequency music
    ├── anger.mp3      # 417 Hz frequency music
    ├── anxiety.mp3    # 396 Hz frequency music
    └── meditation.mp3 # 528 Hz frequency music
```

**Note:** Music files are not included in the repository due to licensing. You can use your own frequency-tuned ambient music or royalty-free alternatives.

### Step 4: Run the Application
```bash
python main.py
```

